# ===== POSTS ===== #

### GET ALL POSTS
GET http://localhost:8000/posts

### GET A POST BY ID
GET http://localhost:8000/posts/2

### POST A POST
POST http://localhost:8000/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "bbbbbbbbbbbbbb",
    "description": "This is bbbbbbbbbbbbbb",
    "media": "img",
    "link": "http://localhost:8000"
}

