PUT http://localhost:8000/posts/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "aaaAAAAA",
    "description": "bBBBBBB",
    "media": "aaaaaaa",
    "link": "aaaaaaa"
}

### DELETE A POST BY ID
DELETE http://localhost:8000/posts/2

